.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc230af31c03bc4e2eed907f58cec9ff5b261b0","tid":1434690,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:49:27.000Z","msg":"好簡單，香港人呢刻未去到呢個位。<br />\n只可以話有呢個諗法既人係呢個時候行得太前，未夠人跟到你既步伐。<br />\n就如睇返10年前陳巧文爬樹都比人屌一樣<br />\n<br />\n當然進步到去呢個位要幾多時間冇人知，但好明顯呢3日未去到"},{"pid":"ced1307c6c63f27e662d65e424b9e3305fa2456c","tid":1434690,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"邊個阻住我搭飛機我屌邊個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce50cdb999437ae4b601bdd38892e40439545052","tid":1434690,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:20:13.000Z","msg":"和理非全面進場"},{"pid":"fc03b9407a51b18a4ef7f432c5a12c09ed297111","tid":1434690,"uid":216279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"廢po咪撚推啦<br />\n識唔識用新功能啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3aeebabb811e593330b7159de3555a27231153","tid":1434690,"uid":226616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"智障仔xd"}]}